11:22.287 --> 11:23.530
know what I'm talking about. Yes, I know. But that 
he didn't really have that incentive. But I want to

11:27.258 --> 11:30.365
know, do you think he did or do you think he didn't? 
He doggone sure did. Because it comes from you,

11:32.810 --> 11:35.596
from your family. Yes, it comes from our family 
tree. And I'll tell you, he loved those people.

11:41.052 --> 11:42.173
Now, he really did. He pushed civil rights from 
JFK. Yes, sir. He pushed it not from JFK. He pushed

