things like that little girls don't nice little 
girls don't get up and leave while the minister's

19:07.008 --> 19:20.781
talking nice little girls Don't interrupt 
services by walking out. Well, I got knees. Now,

19:30.407 --> 19:33.251
that's three things I want you to remember. And I 
got three swats for each of them. That was nine

19:36.195 --> 19:37.317
swats. I remember them. I remember. Every time you 
were also disciplined as a child, you were

19:42.093 --> 19:47.178
disciplined with a principle. Isn't that true? 
That's right. Every time there was a reason for it.

19:51.322 --> 19:53.464
Yeah, that's important. Oh, and I tell you right 
now, I'd rather to have been whipped so many times

19:53.484 --> 19:59.350
than for my daddy to sit down and talk to me. Talking 
to you was worse than getting stanky. He'd set me on

20:02.953 --> 20:07.558
his lap and he'd say, my little princess did me 
wrong. I didn't think that she'd ever do that. And

20:11.705 --> 20:15.291
she... Honey, why did you do that? What made you? 
Oh. I hurt my daddy's feelings. Oh, that was bad.

20:30.056 --> 20:30.998
But again... You know, I think of the things back to 
education and how many years you worked in San

20:32.159 --> 20:37.924
Antonio. How many years again was it? I have it on 
that other tape. I went there in 63 and I left in 73.

20:45.271 --> 20:50.315
73, working with minority children all this time 
or both? Both. I went then over to the Colonies

20:51.436 --> 20:59.343
North, the Butter District, but I still had the 
