21:33.112 --> 21:38.443
You didn't feel like it was a burden to learn 
Spanish so you could teach it, did you? You felt it

21:38.624 --> 21:39.726
was important? I thought it was very important. I 
think it is important today. And let me tell you,

21:43.815 --> 21:50.910
we're the only nation in the world that doesn't 
have two languages taught. The only one. And I

21:52.433 --> 21:53.876
think it's wrong. We need a second language. We do. 
