21:58.325 --> 22:01.251
by. I'm happy. You speak German, you speak 
Spanish, you speak English. That's right. I'm

22:06.882 --> 22:07.524
happy. I have my pen in there from... When

22:13.055 --> 22:31.634
you talk about ranching being a labor of love, you 
love your land, you love your stock, and you enjoy

22:13.055 --> 22:31.634
doing what you're doing. And I don't care where you 
would, my father would take me, he would always

22:32.114 --> 22:43.045
say, look at the land. and get your bearings, you 
came this way. And if you're lost, see what kind of a

22:48.783 --> 22:52.969
tree this is. Is it bent over? Is it straight? Is it a 
mesquite? We didn't have any mesquites in this

22:57.957 --> 23:01.162
country back in 1900. There wasn't any mesquites. 
