1,500 acres. Today, we're poisoning mosquitoes 
on the same land. I want to ask, right, yeah. Why? I

23:20.489 --> 23:21.650
know it's true. The beans are very, very rich in 
protein. And the cattle eat them. The goats eat

23:28.739 --> 23:29.681
them. The horses eat them. Everything eats them. 
