wanted to ask you, what about the grass fires? You 
know, the ones that spread all across the state and

23:50.872 --> 23:55.337
burn for ever and ever? For miles and miles. We've 
had one couple in our county this year, which...

24:03.687 --> 24:11.159
was a misfortune and it was merely an accident. 
